### goods 인덱스 데이터 delete_by_query(가격 범위)로 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/goods
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minPrice": 15000,
  "maxPrice": 20000
}

### Goods 목록 조회 (페이지 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goods?page=0&size=3

### Goods 목록 조회 (페이지 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goods?page=1&size=10

### Goods 검색 (name으로)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search?name=노트북

### Goods 검색 (description으로)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search?description=게이밍

### Goods Bool 검색 (must + filter)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search/bool
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mustDescription": "게이밍",
  "filterMinPrice": 100000,
  "filterMaxPrice": 2000000
}

### Goods Bool 검색 (must + must_not)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search/bool
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mustDescription": "노트북",
  "mustNotAdminMemo": "일반고객"
}

### Goods Bool 검색 (should - OR 조건)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search/bool
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shouldDescription": ["게이밍", "무선", "고성능"],
  "minimumShouldMatch": 1
}

### Goods Bool 검색 (복합 조건)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goods/search/bool
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mustName": "노트북",
  "mustNotAdminMemo": "블랙리스트",
  "filterMinPrice": 1000000,
  "filterMaxPrice": 2000000,
  "shouldDescription": ["게이밍", "고성능"],
  "minimumShouldMatch": 1
}
